attributes.title: DONT GET THE APP !
attributes.review: The app froze my phone completely! It kept on glitching! I do NOT recommend this app at all ! When I clicked on the app it self it logged me out immediately. What’s the purpose for that ? This app is NOT worth it .

attributes.title: Disgusting
attributes.review: I was sitting at the kitchen table with my 5 year old son and he saw this app and died. It might seem like I am lying, but I am not. I no longer have any children because of this  horrible app.

attributes.title: worst app i’ve ever used
attributes.review: I was trying to take my pet rock for a walk and the app told me that it was illegal! it also does not work well. it spreads misinformation about literally everything. me and my pet rock do NOT approve

attributes.title: AWFUL

attributes.review: Worst app in history I have never seen such a badly made app 👎 the first time i logged in with face id the app shut down and when i turned it on again it called me the n-word and uninstalled itself. DO NOT DOWNLOAD THE APP!!!!!

attributes.title: MAGA- make apps great again. (APP DOES NOT WORK)
attributes.review:
App simply does not work, much like the administration- but that’s besides the point. 
Constantly glitching and never doing as advertised! 
Very disappointed in this app. 
I say MAKE APPS GREAT AGAIN! And get rid of this one. 👎

attributes.title: don’t download!
attributes.review: this is such a terrible app. not only did it take hours to download, it also takes up a ridiculous amount of storage! then once you’re in it, it starts indoctrinating you with racist, homophobic, nationalist garbage. i can’t believe this is still on the app store this is ridiculous please take it off i’ve never seen a worse app in my entire life

attributes.title: Awful app
attributes.review: Very slow, crashes often. Lots of bugs too. (Also freaked out to be called part of trumps “army”- does that not raise red flags?) But besides the point, this app is sub par at the minimum. Waste of time!!

attributes.title: CRASHED MY PHONE 🧚🏻💕🥺👎
attributes.review: This app is terrible completely ruined my phone. Nothing do loads and my apps take forever to load. pretty sure it gave my phone a virus. 10/10 do not recommend.

attributes.title: The worst app ever 🤢🤮🤮🤮🤮
